reviewText: I new that my daughter would like Top of the Tots but I wasn't too sure how she would feel about Space Dancing. Since it was only a few dollars difference to get the 2 pack , I took a chance. She loves them both! Actually she seems to like Space Dancing more and parents, let me tell you, the animated version of the Wiggles is a nice break. There are only about 4 songs on the whole DVD and 2 of those songs really aren't that bad.
